{"tid":1819774,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗軍方承認「人為錯誤」　總統Twitter道歉","createTime":"2020-01-11T06:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T07:56:20.000Z","uid":66271,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b3dd2256d6ea352ac7ca0a04be84fe6d14610424","tid":1819774,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e1962df13d12b1ca2b92996.jpg/Da4b2urrm7FgPR3vk8dEgOEy6hHUP3SNv1JJcr9SSXI?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e1962df13d12b1ca2b92996.jpg%2FDa4b2urrm7FgPR3vk8dEgOEy6hHUP3SNv1JJcr9SSXI%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=191a0482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭國際航空公司（Ukraine International Airlines）一架波音737客機8日在伊朗墜毀後，外界一度未能確定其失事原因。有聲音質疑是伊朗意外擊落客機，導致176人慘死。美、英情報指客機是被擊落，而烏克蘭亦指兩國說法「非常可靠」<br />\n<br />\n時隔3天，伊朗國家電視台引述一份軍方聲明報道，稱該國「無意地」（unintentionally）擊落一部烏克蘭國際航空公司客機。聲明是在該國時間1月11日早上發出。<br />\n<br />\n總統魯哈尼（Hassan Rouhani）其後亦於Twitter就事件道歉，他向受影響人士的家屬致以最深刻的慰問，並強調會繼續調查事件及向涉事人員追究責任。<br />\n<br />\n空難發生後翌日、即1月9日，烏克蘭國家安全委員會稱正在調查各種可能原因，包括遭到導彈攻擊、引擎爆炸等。烏克蘭駐伊朗大使館之前曾指，排除事件涉及恐怖主義，但之後改口稱，仍在調查失事原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n伊朗官員在聲明中指出，在客機轉向一個伊朗革命衛隊「敏感的軍方中心」後，軍方誤認它是「敵對目標」。外長扎里夫（Javad Zarif）表示，事件與美伊關係緊張導致伊朗軍方處於「高級準備就緒」的狀態有關"},{"pid":"21d305f6f808ac1777216b130535e1744f78059d","tid":1819774,"uid":69943,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"喺伊朗開出嘅機都可以自己打落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上面有幾多個vip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc15aba4f6512ed6420c3d97a1062acefb850d9","tid":1819774,"uid":14494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:03:45.000Z","msg":"點解唔搵肛蛇過去幫手開記者會"},{"pid":"8efe5d2ac92331d4de7131ace9c15a4ce519d242","tid":1819774,"uid":20870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"所以連識別技術都未夠班。。。"},{"pid":"e5cfb247db771fd02e5f42704e1e1d6c2f333f71","tid":1819774,"uid":191926,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:04:46.000Z","msg":"香港警察學下人地啦<br />\n<br />\n一係唔認<br />\n一係唔道歉<br />\n<br />\n成班人形垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.kinliu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/WhatsApp-Image-2020-01-02-at-10.00.10-AM-768x370.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.kinliu.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2020-01-02-at-10.00.10-AM-768x370.jpeg&h=53b5e58d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n望之不似人形"},{"pid":"8c03f9a70f31e04518c2dd1e1e9a765f8307ec18","tid":1819774,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:08:22.000Z","msg":"我深紅老豆前晚仲話美國打爆隻機想屈伊朗做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住又話會美國打伊朗唔得閒理中國，中共又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58830925d048e85e38da38c3d6b1833e1d13694","tid":1819774,"uid":261937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:15:08.000Z","msg":"做錯就認，似返個人。<br />\n清算黑警，刻不容緩。"},{"pid":"b86b40506376b606b09bcd1012f33b92178b7901","tid":1819774,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:18:12.000Z","msg":"sor lo"},{"pid":"3742eaa26f78f583d086a77ea2be9514e446825c","tid":1819774,"uid":81150,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:22:08.000Z","msg":"原諒佢了<br />\n<br />\n俾佢走啦   失民意架"},{"pid":"a3693a0f10828e6c18859d40309fc608e541dfa8","tid":1819774,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:22:19.000Z","msg":"伊朗航空 655"},{"pid":"2b5203d1e039e52db402b6610fbe3afed7c8fb9d","tid":1819774,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3742eaa26f78f583d086a77ea2be9514e446825c","tid":1819774,"uid":81150,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score